#: ../../source/wapt-security/security-install-kerberos.rst:85
msgid ""
"If the authentication request is successful, you can then create your "
"HTTP Keytab with the :program:`msktutil` command."
msgstr ""
"Si la requête d'authentification est réussie, vous pouvez créer votre "
"HTTP Keytab avec la commande :program:`msktutil`."

#: ../../source/wapt-security/security-install-kerberos.rst:88
msgid ""
"Be sure to modify the *<DOMAIN_CONTROLER>* string with the name of your "
"domain controller (eg: **srvads.mydomain.lan**)."
msgstr ""
"Assurez-vous de modifier l'entrée *<DOMAIN_CONTROLER>* avec le nom de "
"votre contrôleur de domaine (eg: **srvads.mydomain.lan**)."

#: ../../source/wapt-security/security-install-kerberos.rst:98
msgid ""
"Be sure to have properly configured your WAPT Server *hostname* before "
"running these commands;"
msgstr ""
"Assurez-vous d'avoir correctement configuré le nom du serveur WAPT avant "
"de lancer ces commandes;"

#: ../../source/wapt-security/security-install-kerberos.rst:101
msgid ""
"In order to double check your *hostname*, you can run :code:`echo "
"$(hostname)` and it must return the name that will be used by WAPT agent "
